caption.title: Phylogenetic analysis of the HA gene segment of Palestinian influenza A(H3N2) isolates.
caption.p: Palestinian HA sequences (in red) were compared with those from regional and international isolates, as well as vaccine strain of seasons 2014/2015-2017/2018 (in dark blue). NCBI and GISAID accession numbers are indicated for all archived sequences. HA1 aa substitutions are in green and HA2 are in green and underlined.
